cast.overview: Samantha Kingston has everything. Then, everything changes. After one fateful night, she wakes up with no future at all. Trapped into reliving the same day over and over, she begins to question just how perfect her life really was.
cast.title: Before I Fall

details.biography: Claire Margaret Corlett was born on July 9, 1999. She is an actress and writer, known for My Little Pony: Friendship Is Magic (2010), Dinosaur Train (2009), To All the Boys: P.S. I Still Love You (2020) and Dinosaur Train: Adventure Island (2021).
details.name: Claire Margaret Corlett
